Create a web application using HTML, Javascript for a forum discussion panel.
The user should be able to add posts regarding a query. Input values will be a question and topic of question. There will be two buttons
add and get details.

After clicking the add button the posts should be stored in the local storage of the browser and should be displayed in a tabular format.
After clicking the get details button the user should be shown how much post did he create regarding a particular topic.

Note: If the above tasks are achieved then you can beautify the web application using CSS which will be awarded extra points
